    <thetext>Description of problem:
When reinstalling system with blivet-gui and chosing pre-existing partition (like /boot) after choosing to &quot;Set mountpoint&quot; (/boot) the choice is forgotten when selecting format choice.

Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
Fedora 26 Alpha
anaconda 26.21.1-1

How reproducible:
always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. Start re-installation, use blivet-gui.
2. Chose existing partition (like former /boot)
3. Chose &quot;Set mountpoint&quot; and assign a mountpoint (/boot)
4. Choose format

Actual results:
The previously configured mountpoint is forgotten.

Expected results:
In format dialog is the mountpoint pre-filled with data from before.</thetext>
